    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch to be found and it still has that fresh new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look or go for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
