      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing system. This specimen is an absolute survivor, retaining its factory-correct 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a pristine limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptional, with no signs of subframe fatigue and all suspension bushings maintaining original factory compliance. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior leather retains its original matte texture without the typical bolster degradation. Every mechanical system, from the cooling loop to the electronic throttle actuators, functions within peak operating parameters, making this a turn-key acquisition for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
